Description_lang: Conceals you in the shadows until cancelled, allowing you to stalk enemies without being seen. $?s14062[Movement speed while stealthed is increased by $s3% and damage dealt is increased by $s4%.]?s108209[ Abilities cost $112942s1% less while stealthed. ][]$?s31223[ Attacks from Stealth and for $31223s1 sec after deal $31665s1% more damage.][]

description_blz.en_US: Conceals you in the shadows until cancelled, allowing you to stalk enemies without being seen.
description_blz.es_MX: Te esconde en las sombras hasta que se cancela, lo que te permite acechar a tus enemigos sin que te vean.
description_blz.pt_BR: Esconde você em sombras até ser cancelado, permitindo que você espreite inimigos sem ser visto.
description_blz.de_DE: Verbirgt Euch bis Abbruch in den Schatten, wodurch Ihr um Gegner herumschleichen könnt, ohne gesehen zu werden.
description_blz.en_GB: Conceals you in the shadows until cancelled, allowing you to stalk enemies without being seen.
description_blz.es_ES: Te oculta en las sombras hasta que se cancela, lo que te permite acechar a los enemigos sin que te vean.
description_blz.fr_FR: Vous dissimule dans les ombres jusqu’à annulation, vous permettant de traquer les ennemis sans être vu.
description_blz.it_IT: Attiva la modalità furtiva fino all'annullamento, permettendoti di seguire i nemici senza essere visto.
description_blz.ru_RU: Сливается с тенями, чтобы незаметно подкрадываться к противникам. Действует до отмены.
description_blz.ko_KR: 그림자 속에 숨어 취소할 때까지 보이지 않는 상태로 적을 추적할 수 있습니다.
description_blz.zh_TW: 潛入暗影之中，使你能夠在不被發現的情況下追蹤敵人，直到主動取消。
description_blz.zh_CN: 使你进入潜行状态直到取消为止，悄悄地接近敌人而不被发现。
